Then there would have been no
dead Turks lying around.

261
00:36:12.560 --> 00:36:14.880
And then your sales market had gone
gone times 100.

262
00:36:16.440 --> 00:36:18.320
I didn't fuck that shit up.

263
00:36:19.480 --> 00:36:21.320
You know that if you send me
to Germany...

264
00:36:21.440 --> 00:36:23.880
that I'm not going to sit on my hands
waiting for something to go wrong.

265
00:36:24.000 --> 00:36:26.800
You know I trade.
That's what I do.

266
00:36:28.040 --> 00:36:29.840
So what are you going to do? Hmm?

267
00:36:31.840 --> 00:36:33.600
Are we going to pick up where
we left off?

268
00:36:35.200 --> 00:36:37.520
Or will you let him put a bullet
through my head?

269
00:37:04.760 --> 00:37:08.000
What? To where?
No one needs to know.

270
00:37:09.160 --> 00:37:10.800
Just her.

271
00:37:12.920 --> 00:37:15.880
Tonight now all contact
through you.

272
00:37:16.000 --> 00:37:17.720
And no one else.

273
00:37:19.720 --> 00:37:21.280
Is good.

274
00:37:21.400 --> 00:37:23.120
Take it with you.

275
00:39:34.600 --> 00:39:36.280
Samira?
